# <%= project %> тАФ Ticket Workflow

## Stages

| Stage | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| `0-ideas` | Lightweight ideas тАФ not yet tickets |
| `1-backlog` | Tickets waiting to be prioritized |
| `2-ready-for-refinement` | Prioritized, needs plan + test cases |
| `3-ready-for-development` | Refined with plan, ready to build |
| `4-in-progress` | Engineer is actively working |
| `5-peer-review` | Code complete, awaiting peer review |
| `6-ready-for-testing` | Peer approved, awaiting QE |
| `7-ready-for-release` | QE approved, ready to ship |
| `8-needs-rework` | Rejected тАФ see QE/review notes |
| `9-blocked` | Cannot proceed тАФ blocker documented |
| `10-released` | Shipped and verified |

## Ticket Structure

Each ticket lives in a folder: `<%= tickets_dir %>/{stage}/{ID}--{slug}/`

Contents:
- `ticket.md` тАФ Metadata, description, acceptance criteria, history
- `test-cases.md` тАФ QE test cases (added during refinement)
- `plan.md` тАФ Implementation plan (added during refinement)
- `screenshots/` тАФ Evidence from QE testing

## Commands

| Action | Command |
|--------|---------|
| Create ticket | `bobby create -t "Title" --type feature -p medium` |
| Create idea | `bobby idea "Quick thought"` |
| Promote idea | `bobby promote IDEA-001` |
| View board | `bobby list` |
| View ticket | `bobby view TKT-001` |
| Move to refinement | `bobby refine TKT-001` |
| Mark ready | `bobby ready TKT-001` |
| Start work | `bobby start TKT-001` |
| Submit for review | `bobby review TKT-001` |
| Approve review | `bobby peer-approve TKT-001` |
| Reject review | `bobby peer-reject TKT-001 "reason"` |
| QE approve | `bobby approve TKT-001` |
| QE reject | `bobby reject TKT-001 "reason"` |
| Release | `bobby release TKT-001` |
| Reopen | `bobby reopen TKT-001` |
| Block | `bobby block TKT-001 "reason"` |
| Unblock | `bobby unblock TKT-001` |

## Health Checks

<% if (health_checks && health_checks.length > 0) { %>
<% health_checks.forEach(function(check) { %>
- **<%= check.name %>**: <%= check.url %> тАФ <%= check.description || '' %>
<% }); %>
<% } else { %>
_No health checks configured._
<% } %>

## Retrospectives

When a systemic issue is found:
1. `bobby retro TKT-001 "pattern name"` тАФ creates a retro in `<%= tickets_dir %>/retrospectives/`
2. Fill in the problem, root cause, and fix
3. `bobby learn bobby-build "pattern" "description"` тАФ adds to the skill's learnings

This feedback loop is what makes Bobby get smarter over time.
